cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE 

The paper discusses machine learning approaches to computer vision, specifically semantic labeling, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of deep learning (cs.LG) and learning from constraints (cs.AI). The proposed framework also involves lifelong learning (cs.RO) and deep architectures (cs.NE).
